<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262>
    bibo:endPage "68" ;
    bibo:journal "ZooKeys" ;
    bibo:startPage "47" ;
    bibo:volume "997" ;
    dc:creator "Quintero-Gutierrez, Edwin Javier; Sandmann, Dorothee; Combita-Heredia, Orlando; Klarner, Bernhard; Widyastuti, Rahayu; Scheu, Stefan" ;
    dc:date "2020" ;
    dc:title "Review of the mite genus Krantzolaspina Datta & Bhattacharjee (Mesostigmata, Parholaspididae) with re-description of K. angustatus comb. nov. (Ishikawa) from Indonesia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure1>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure6>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure2>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure3>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure4>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure5> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure1>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. Dorsal idiosoma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479381" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure6>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. A-D Legs I-IV, respectively. Coxae I-IV in the Fig. 2." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479386" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. Ventral idiosoma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479382" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure3>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. Ventral idiosoma showing the sternometasternal, genitiventrianal and parapodal shield. A Holotype of Krantzolaspina angustatus B Paratype of Indutolaelaps jiroftensis syn. nov., photos by Raphael Castilho C New material from Indonesia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479383" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female, Gnathosomal structures. Holotype (Left); Indutolaelaps jiroftensis syn. nov. (Middle), photos by Raphael Castilho; New material from Indonesia (Right). A-C Subcapitulum D-F Epistome G-I Chelicera J-L Palp trochanter with a ventral spine-like process." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479384" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.997.54262.figure5>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Krantzolaspina angustatus comb. nov., adult female. Palp, note the ventral spine-like process in palptrochanter." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/479385" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

